### Block a user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/blocked-users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user124",
  "blockedBy": "admin456",
  "blockReason": "Violation of terms of service"
}

### Get all blocked users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/blocked-users

### Unblock a user (replace {id} with actual document ID from block response)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/blocked-users/ae5310d2-1d54-4558-a9d5-0609d1442471

### Example: Block another user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/blocked-users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user789",
  "blockedBy": "moderator001",
  "blockReason": "Spam activity detected"
}
